children.name: Errors by Region
children.searchQuery:
$$Cloudtrail SQS
| json field=_raw "eventSource"
| json field=_raw "userIdentity.type"
| json field=_raw "userIdentity.arn"
| parse "\"userName\":\"*\"" as user 
| parse "\"eventName\":\"*\"" as event_name
| json field=_raw "awsRegion"
| json field=_raw "errorCode"
| json field=_raw "errorMessage"
| where eventSource matches "sqs*"
| count as count by errorcode, awsregion
| sort count

children.name: SQS Event Trend
children.searchQuery:
$$Cloudtrail SQS
| json field=_raw "eventSource"
| json field=_raw "userIdentity.type"
| json field=_raw "userIdentity.arn"
| parse "\"userName\":\"*\"" as user 
| parse "\"eventName\":\"*\"" as event_name
| where eventSource matches "sqs*"
| timeslice 1h
| count as count by event_name, _timeslice
| transpose row _timeslice column event_name

children.name: SQS Events
children.searchQuery:
$$Cloudtrail SQS
| json field=_raw "eventSource"
| json field=_raw "userIdentity.type"
| json field=_raw "userIdentity.arn"
| parse "\"userName\":\"*\"" as user 
| parse "\"eventName\":\"*\"" as event_name
| where eventSource matches "sqs*"
| timeslice 1m
| count as count by event_name, user, %useridentity.type, _timeslice

children.name: SQS Events by User
children.searchQuery:
$$Cloudtrail SQS
| json field=_raw "eventSource"
| json field=_raw "userIdentity.type"
| json field=_raw "userIdentity.arn"
| parse "\"userName\":\"*\"" as user 
| parse "\"eventName\":\"*\"" as event_name
| where eventSource matches "sqs*"
//| timeslice 1h
| count as count by user, event_name
| transpose row user column event_name
